# Empirebuilder Codex Architecture

> **“A living blueprint that turns systems into fortunes – the next decade is built on architecture, not hype.”**

## What’s Included

- Modular Node.js API (templates → PDF, JWT auth, logging)
- Dockerfile & CI/CD (GitHub Actions)
- Immutable build log for every decision
- Pre-built templates (business plan, contract negotiation)
- Assets (branded logo)
- Ready to deploy or sell as a premium starter kit

## Quickstart

```bash
# Clone and enter
git clone <YOUR-REPO-URL> empirebuilder-
cd empirebuilder-/income

# Install & run
npm install
cp .env.example .env  # (set your JWT secret)
node api/index.js

# Or run Docker (from project root)
docker build -t codex-income ./income
docker run -p 3000:3000 codex-income
